<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٠٥٠ -<span class="c5"> وَأَمَّا ابْنُ جُرَيْجٍ فَقَالَ:</span> حُدِّثْتُ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ عُمَرَ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّهُ كَانَ يَتَعَوَّذُ بَيْنَ الرُّكْنِ وَالْبَابِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>